snippet.title: Warner Bros DOUBLE DOWN Amber Heard Mera Replacing Aquaman In Justice League Scene
snippet.description:
Warner Bros DOUBLE DOWN Amber Heard Mera Replacing Aquaman In Justice League Scene



per boundingintocomics - Amber Heard is sticking around as Mera and may have a future as a dominant recurring female in the DC Extended Universe. She’s rumored to have taken part in the reshoots conducted recently by Zack Snyder to finish Justice League, and there’s more.


https://boundingintocomics.com/2020/12/09/rumor-amber-heards-mera-to-replace-jason-momoas-aquaman-in-pivotal-scene-in-zack-snyders-justice-league/
